You must now figure out where that RPM stashed the plugin :-) Once you find it make a symbolic link in your ~/.mozilla/plugins directory to it like this:<br />
ln -s /location/of/mozilla/plugin ~/.mozilla/pluginsThanks very much!<a href="http://java.com/en/download/help/5000010500.xml#rpm" target="_blank">http://java.com/en/download/help/5000010500.xml#rpm</a><br />
