The RPM install file works on pretty much all modern Linux distributions that support RPM. The distros listed are ones known to work with this java package, and I have seen it working on Mandrake  10.0, 10.1 and Mandriva 2005.<br />
<br />
Download the latest RPM from <a href="http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.5.0/download.jsp" target="_blank">http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.5.0/download.jsp</a><br />
